title: Large 1 Bedroom for August. Side by side walk in closets.
posting_body: ['This apartment is a great value with heat paid and free laundry!', 'It has a nice quiet view on the back side of our building!', 'Hurry in today!', '\uf0d8 Free Laundry on every floor', '\uf0d8', 'Balcony', '\uf0d8', 'A/C in unit', '\uf0d8 Heat and Water Included in rent', '\uf0d8', 'Off street parking', '\uf0d8', 'Garages available for rent', '\uf0d8', 'Secured building', '\uf0d8', 'On-site Staff', '\uf0d8 Professionally managed by Lifeline Properties', 'This apartment is close to I-94 so it is easy to get to just about anywhere.', 'Downtown St. Paul is just a short drive down the road.', '3M is a few minutes away in the other direction.', 'U of M is only 14 minutes away.', 'Battle Creek Regional Park is less than 2 miles away and can be reached in a 5 minute drive.', 'We would love an opportunity to show you what our property has to offer you!', 'Stop in for a tour or give Brian a call at', 'show contact info', '!', 'Office hours are 1:00-5pm Monday thru Friday.']
